{"tid":351066,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實audit以外可以做咩？","createTime":"2017-08-07T16:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T23:23:22.000Z","uid":62286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d3734b240c95823bab805dc1dc2e4193b060f9","tid":351066,"uid":62286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:47:42.000Z","msg":"身為非三大accounting grad，除咗入big4, 2nd tier, local，條路仲可以點？<br />\n<br />\n我係一間大local度做，OT大概到7:30至9點，對比其他firm，可能算輕鬆，但人工得10.5k。再望望啲同事，做咗4,5年先得20k左右。<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話去2nd tier, 去big4，無錯，人工當然會好，但更加唔洗收工，無人生。<br />\n<br />\n再同中學同學對比一下，當年入ive 讀工程相關嘅HD嘅同學仔，係我year3時，已經拎緊的20-30k人工。 然後又有人話，點同呢，你考完QP有個牌，想轉去commercial; 兩三萬一個月，走唔甩啦！<br />\n<br />\n咁其實咁辛苦做乜？我依家去做其他行業都有兩萬啦。我都係想辛苦得值得，audit好似當人傻仔咁，&quot;俾你學嘢啊！&quot; &quot;俾你攞經驗&quot; &quot;捱到你就成功人士&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟，有無其他岀路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSorry, 入世未深，怨下而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919a138c6248788b513ce8c4900f930af942922c","tid":351066,"uid":30696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:12:55.000Z","msg":"local公價咁低？"},{"pid":"147441fed092f7d4a97f4a23c0116712f2a2599a","tid":351066,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>local公價咁低？</blockquote><br />\nlocal係咁低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 非3大acct fg 同樓主一樣反思緊"},{"pid":"fb94a6abfdee91e54e0e41a1d7c9a171fae27b32","tid":351066,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:20:10.000Z","msg":"local firm狗先做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52c377e8f1954e71536056c284d1098c75642c8","tid":351066,"uid":66500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomo